Multi-Tenant AI Voice Platform (Enterprise Upgrade)
1️⃣ Objective

Convert the existing single-client Voice Agent project into a multi-tenant enterprise SaaS platform owned and operated by Codeless Technologies.

Core Principles

One shared infrastructure

Single PostgreSQL database

Strict tenant isolation via tenant_id

Per-tenant OpenAI API keys

Centralized master admin (Codeless only)

Widget-based client integration

Docker-based production deployment

