3️⃣ Tenant Model

Each company = one tenant.

Isolation is enforced by:

tenant_id column in every data table

Middleware validation on every API request

Per-tenant OpenAI API key stored securely

Origin validation for widget calls

4️⃣ Database Schema (Multi-Tenant)
4.1 tenants
Field	Type	Description
id	UUID	Primary Tenant ID
company_name	string	Company Name
domain	string	Allowed domain
avatar_id	UUID	Selected avatar
introduction_script	text	Greeting
voice_model	string	OpenAI voice
openai_api_key_encrypted	text	Tenant-specific key
status	active/suspended	
created_at	timestamp	
4.2 knowledge_base
Field	Type
id	UUID
tenant_id	UUID
category	string
title	string
content	text
4.3 conversations
Field	Type
id	UUID
tenant_id	UUID
session_id	string
transcript	text
response	text
token_usage	integer
duration	float
created_at	timestamp
4.4 avatars
Field	Type
id	UUID
name	string
image_url	string
default_voice	string
personality_prompt	text
5️⃣ Tenant Resolution Strategy

All widget requests must include:

Headers:
X-Tenant-ID: <uuid>
X-Signature: <hmac_signature>

Backend middleware:

Validate tenant exists

Validate signature

Validate request origin

Inject tenant-specific OpenAI API key

Attach tenant context to request

No API call is processed without valid tenant context.

6️⃣ Per-Tenant OpenAI API Keys

Each tenant has:

Separate OpenAI API key

Stored encrypted in database

Decrypted only during request processing

Used exclusively for that tenant’s requests

Example logic:

openai_client = OpenAI(api_key=tenant.api_key)

This ensures:

No cross-billing

No cross-token leakage

Independent usage tracking

7️⃣ Admin Control Model

Currently:

Only Codeless has dashboard access

Clients do not log in

Codeless manages:

Tenant creation

Avatar assignment

Knowledge base

API key configuration

Activation / suspension

Future (Phase 2):

Tenant self-service dashboard

Subscription billing

8️⃣ Widget Deployment Model

Clients only receive:

<script>
window.VOICE_AGENT_TENANT_ID = "uuid";
window.VOICE_AGENT_SIGNATURE = "generated_signature";
</script>
<script src="https://ai.codeless.ai/widget.js"></script>

Client responsibility:

Paste script into website

Codeless responsibility:

Infrastructure

AI processing

Logging

Scaling

Security

Monitoring

